://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4888952422655402e-31, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9929962726999756, \"rank\": 0.007053121458372818, \"text\": \"La D\\u00e9fense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lovely sunshine\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"the residential areas\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2727}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2812}, {\"ngram\": \"the district\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A commitment to green spaces is a key part of the area's transformation project, which was launched at the end of 2021, to make La D\\u00e9fense 'the first post-carbon global business district.'\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A commitment\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"green spaces\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"a key part\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"the area's transformation project\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"La D\\u00e9fense\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities in the area have committed to halving greenhouse gas emissions by 2030.\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Authorities\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3031}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"greenhouse gas emissions\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another of the the objectives is to make the area greener - and the 11 acre park I walked through provided an opportunity for peace and quiet, an ideal respite if you have a busy schedule of Olympic events to watch.\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"the the objectives\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3134}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3154}, {\"ngram\": \"the 11 acre park\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3185}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3236}, {\"ngram\": \"quiet, an ideal respite\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"a busy schedule\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic events\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was also a great view of the Eiffel Tower and you are in the shadow of the Grande Arche, the result of a national design competition, built in 1982 as a 20th century take on the Arc de Triomphe.\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3403, \"end\": 3415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grande_Arche\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grande Arche\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grande_Arche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grande_Arche\"}, {\"begin\": 3506, \"end\": 3521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5405658533317542e-28, \"text\": \"Arc de Triomphe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great view\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3349}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3369}, {\"ngram\": \"the shadow\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3427}, {\"ngram\": \"a national design competition\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3460}, {\"ngram\": \"a 20th century take\", \"from\": 3479, \"to\": 3498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's certainly an impressive structure, but my only disappointment was that the observation deck is closed to visitors (as it has been, permanently, since April 2023due to the 'colossal operating cost' of the building) meaning I had to make do with a view from below.\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an impressive structure\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3562}, {\"ngram\": \"my only disappointment\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3590}, {\"ngram\": \"the observation deck\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3642}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3684}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'colossal operating cost\", \"from\": 3696, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"the building\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3741}, {\"ngram\": \"a view\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearby there is the enormous Westfield Les 4 Temps, with its 238 shops, perfect if you want to escape the heat and enjoy the aircon - and the French shopping.\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3822, \"end\": 3831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Westfield_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0457162479559729e-24, \"text\": \"Westfield\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Westfield_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Westfield_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 3935, \"end\": 3941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9992293530958494, \"rank\": 0.0007678419313596266, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its 238 shops\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3863}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3903}, {\"ngram\": \"the aircon\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, each year, the area is home to annual festivals.\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 4006, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"annual festivals\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Garden Parvis pop up, at the foot of the Grande Arche is described as an 'urban oasis' where visitors and residents can unwind, and is open until July 26.\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4052, \"end\": 4064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grande_Arche\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grande Arche\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grande_Arche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grande_Arche\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Garden Parvis\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4024}, {\"ngram\": \"the foot\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4044}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'urban oasis\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4096}, {\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4112}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4126}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A programme of events includes DJ sets, comedy, and quizzes.\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A programme\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4177}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4187}, {\"ngram\": \"DJ sets\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4204}, {\"ngram\": \"comedy\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4212}, {\"ngram\": \"quizzes\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is also the Jazz Festival, running to June 30, which is in its 47thyear.\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Jazz Festival\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4259}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 4272, \"to\": 4276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a series of open-air concerts - all of which are completely free.\", \"from\": 4307, \"to\": 4381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 4316, \"to\": 4324}, {\"ngram\": \"open-air concerts\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want to stay in the action during the Olympics, La D\\u00e9fense boasts around 2,600 hotel rooms.\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4438, \"end\": 4448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9929962726999756, \"rank\": 0.007053121458372818, \"text\": \"La D\\u00e9fense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4416}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4436}, {\"ngram\": \"around 2,600 hotel rooms\", \"from\": 4456, \"to\": 4480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of these belong to the top-of-the-range hotel chains such as Hilton and CitizenM.\", \"from\": 4482, \"to\": 4568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4548, \"end\": 4554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.254534866676616e-43, \"text\": \"Hilton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the-range\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4526}, {\"ngram\": \"CitizenM.\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the big perks of the area however is how accessible it is from thecentre of Paris.\", \"from\": 4570, \"to\": 4659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4653, \"end\": 4658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3938417360989964e-41, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the big perks\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4590}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 4594, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"thecentre\", \"from\": 4640, \"to\": 4649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arena staff told us that 80% of attendees come via public transport, something they can determine by monitoring footfall in the nearby, spacious La D\\u00e9fense Metro station.\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4805, \"end\": 4815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9929962766529531, \"rank\": 0.007053121458372818, \"text\": \"La D\\u00e9fense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arena staff\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4677, \"to\": 4679}, {\"ngram\": \"80%\", \"from\": 4685, \"to\": 4688}, {\"ngram\": \"attendees\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4701}, {\"ngram\": \"public transport\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4727}, {\"ngram\": \"footfall\", \"from\": 4772, \"to\": 4780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I stayed in the three starHotel Lucien & Marinetteright by Gare Du Nord where the Eurostar comes in.\", \"from\": 4832, \"to\": 4932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4891, \"end\": 4903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_du_Nord\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0254073468330225e-26, \"text\": \"Gare Du Nord\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_du_Nord\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gare_du_Nord\"}, {\"begin\": 4914, \"end\": 4922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.926004574633441e-22, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the three starHotel Lucien\", \"from\": 4844, \"to\": 4870}, {\"ngram\": \"Marinetteright\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the Olympics, the cost of a double room comes in at \\u20ac278 euros (\\u00a3235) per night - more expensive than you usually expect for a hotel room in Paris considering prior the games you can get the same at the hotel for under \\u20ac150 (\\u00a3127) per night.\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 5181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5081, \"end\": 5086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3938417360989964e-41, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 4952}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 4954, \"to\": 4962}, {\"ngram\": \"a double room\", \"from\": 4966, \"to\": 4979}, {\"ngram\": \"euros\", \"from\": 4997, \"to\": 5002}, {\"ngram\": \"a hotel room\", \"from\": 5065, \"to\": 5077}, {\"ngram\": \"prior the games\", \"from\": 5099, \"to\": 5114}, {\"ngram\": \"the hotel\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5148}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 5175, \"to\": 5180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, it's nearly half the current price of a night in the cheapest room in the Hilton in La D\\u00e9fense during this period, so certainly a more affordable alternative.\", \"from\": 5183, \"to\": 5350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5266, \"end\": 5272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.254534866676616e-43, \"text\": \"Hilton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hilton_Worldwide\"}, {\"begin\": 5276, \"end\": 5286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9929962726999756, \"rank\": 0.007053121458372818, \"text\": \"La D\\u00e9fense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nearly half the current price\", \"from\": 5197, \"to\": 5226}, {\"ngram\": \"a night\", \"from\": 5230, \"to\": 5237}, {\"ngram\": \"the cheapest room\", \"from\": 5241, \"to\": 5258}, {\"ngram\": \"this period\", \"from\": 5294, \"to\": 5305}, {\"ngram\": \"so certainly a more affordable alternative\", \"from\": 5307, \"to\": 5349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The biggest plus for me was that I stayed in the heart of Paris, with easy access to all the world-famous highlights, from the Eiffel Tower to the quintessential Parisian bistros.\", \"from\": 5352, \"to\": 5531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5410, \"end\": 5415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3938417360989964e-41, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The biggest plus\", \"from\": 5352, \"to\": 5368}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 5397, \"to\": 5406}, {\"ngram\": \"easy access\", \"from\": 5422, \"to\": 5433}, {\"ngram\": \"all the world-famous highlights\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5468}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 5475, \"to\": 5491}, {\"ngram\": \"the quintessential Parisian bistros\", \"from\": 5495, \"to\": 5530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For all the Londoners heading to Wembley to see our girl this weekend, you are in for a treat.\", \"from\": 5533, \"to\": 5627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5566, \"end\": 5573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wembley_Stadium\", \"score\": 0.9759831162708192, \"rank\": 0.019371265007382434, \"text\": \"Wembley\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wembley_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wembley_Stadium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the Londoners\", \"from\": 5537, \"to\": 5554}, {\"ngram\": \"our girl\", \"from\": 5581, \"to\": 5589}, {\"ngram\": \"a treat\", \"from\": 5619, \"to\": 5626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having seen the recording of the Eras Tour onDisney+more times than I care to admit, I was most excited to see the newly added The Tortured Poets Department section.\", \"from\": 5629, \"to\": 5794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the recording\", \"from\": 5641, \"to\": 5654}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eras Tour\", \"from\": 5658, \"to\": 5671}, {\"ngram\": \"the newly added The Tortured Poets Department section\", \"from\": 5740, \"to\": 5793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The crowd was on fire too - the noise from the audience just after Taylor finished Champagne Problems, which seemed to get louder and louder for at least five minutes, will be a core memory from now on.\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5879, \"end\": 5897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champagne_Problems_(Taylor_Swift_song)\", \"score\": 0.812273899662596, \"rank\": 0.23111111111108376, \"text\": \"Champagne Problems\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champagne_Problems_(Taylor_Swift_song)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champagne_Problems_(Taylor_Swift_song)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The crowd\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5805}, {\"ngram\": \"fire\", \"from\": 5813, \"to\": 5817}, {\"ngram\": \"the noise\", \"from\": 5824, \"to\": 5833}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 5839, \"to\": 5851}, {\"ngram\": \"Taylor\", \"from\": 5863, \"to\": 5869}, {\"ngram\": \"at least five minutes\", \"from\": 5941, \"to\": 5962}, {\"ngram\": \"a core memory\", \"from\": 5972, \"to\": 5985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taylor herself was so stunned, she took off her earpiece to her us roar.\", \"from\": 5999, \"to\": 6071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Taylor\", \"from\": 5999, \"to\": 6005}, {\"ngram\": \"her earpiece\", \"from\": 6043, \"to\": 6055}, {\"ngram\":