speedy and efficient, with the arena looking very empty even minutes after Taylor ended.\", \"from\": 8241, \"to\": 8351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 8290, \"to\": 8299}, {\"ngram\": \"Taylor\", \"from\": 8338, \"to\": 8344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not help but compare it to my experience two years ago seeing Red Hot Chili Peppers at Stade de France where it took about an hour to filter through the crowds and police barriers - at La D\\u00e9fense, the exit strategy seemed far more optimised.\", \"from\": 8352, \"to\": 8601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8422, \"end\": 8443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Hot Chili Peppers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\"}, {\"begin\": 8545, \"end\": 8555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"score\": 0.9929962726999756, \"rank\": 0.007053121458372818, \"text\": \"La D\\u00e9fense\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_D\\u00e9fense\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my experience\", \"from\": 8387, \"to\": 8400}, {\"ngram\": \"Stade de France\", \"from\": 8447, \"to\": 8462}, {\"ngram\": \"about an hour\", \"from\": 8477, \"to\": 8490}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds and police barriers\", \"from\": 8509, \"to\": 8539}, {\"ngram\": \"the exit strategy\", \"from\": 8557, \"to\": 8574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day I was back at the arena as the Eras stage came down.\", \"from\": 8603, \"to\": 8668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 8630, \"to\": 8639}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eras stage\", \"from\": 8643, \"to\": 8657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic organisers got the keys to the venue on May 15, an